text: Sandeep Kirtane (born 27 October 1973) is an Indian professional tennis player. He made his ATP Tour debut at the 1996 India Open, where he lost in the 1st round to Sandon Stolle. ==References== ==External Links== Category:Indian male tennis players Category:Living people Category:1973 births Category:Racket sportspeople from Pune
